data.description: Price Improvement! Dont miss this opportunity. Welcome to this Luxurious and well-located townhome located in the highly desired Econ Trails Community. This modern home was recently built in 2019! This gorgeous two-story home offers ample space with 3 bedrooms and the 2 bathrooms plus another half bathroom promises to offer the convenience you deserve. This thoughtfully designed home has a gorgeous kitchen with stainless steel appliances, 42" cabinets, stunning and durable quartz countertops, and beautiful tile floors. The bathrooms are elegantly appointed with quartz countertops as well as a modern look and feel. The large plank tile was tastefully placed in the wet and common areas. The bedrooms have plush carpets and the large closets will surprise you. inside laundry is exactly what you need, plus a garage to keep your car looking as new as this house. upgraded features such as Wi-Fi certification a covered lanai with an acrylic deck, and 2" faux wood blinds make this home the perfect fit for all your needs. Econ Trails is a gated community featuring a swimming pool & cabana, picnic pavilion, tot lot, recreation areas, and fitness trail  Located right around the corner from UCF, Valencia College, and just 15-20 mins to Downtown, and Orlando Int'l Airport. Close access to the 408 and 417 expressways makes it a breeze to commute anywhere in Central Florida. WATERFORD LAKES SHOPPING CENTER, AdventHealth, and Lake Nona Medical City are all just a few minutes away. Call to schedule a showing today.
